治愈，我的意思是它仍在发生，我仍在努力解决。”</p><p>早些时候，比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）和绿色日<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">（Billie Eilish）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">绿日（Green Day</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-join-green-day-for-last-night-on-earth-at-la-fireaid-concert-3833458">）在场地上进行了现场演绎</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>幸存的成员 -  Krist Novoselic， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">Dave Grohl</a>和Pat Smear <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-surviving-members-of-nirvana-reunite-with-joan-jett-kim-gordon-and-st-vincent-at-la-fires-benefit-concert-3833434">在起亚论坛上也出人意料地露面</a>。</p><p>这三人与圣文森特<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">（St. Vincent）</a>一起进行了涅rv，与金·戈登<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-gordon">（Kim Gordon）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joan-jett">琼·杰特（Joan Jett）</a>的“学校”和“领土小便”一起进行了“学校”，而格罗尔（Grohl）的女儿紫罗兰（Grohl）的女儿紫罗兰（Mic）则将麦克风带来“所有道歉”。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_stvincent_nirvana_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">圣文森特（St. Vincent）在2025年1月30日在起亚论坛举行的FireAid Benefit Concers中与尼尔瓦纳（Nirvana）的Pat Smear，Dave Grohl和Krist Novoselic一起演出，2025年，Scott Dudelson/Getty Images。</figcaption></figure><p>晚上演出的其他艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rod-stewart">Rod Stewart</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-perry">Katy Perry</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">Joni Mitchell</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">Sting</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">Stevie Nicks</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">Gracie Abrams</a> ， 