拉娜·德尔·雷伊（Lana del Rey）是周末的“明天快点”的“深渊”的隐藏功能https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-hidden-feature-the-the-abyss-the-weeknd-hurry-hurry-tomorrow-tomorrow-383499?utm_source = rsss＆utm_medium = rsssssssssssssss间Del-Rey隐藏在the-abyss-weeknd-hurry-tomareLiberty Dunworth Fri, 31 Jan 2025 11:05:43 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3833499 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亚伯“ the the Weeknd” Tesfaye和Lana del Rey" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>专辑中的其他合作来自Travis Scott，Future，Florence + The Machine，Playboi Carti和Anitta</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-hidden-feature-on-the-abyss-the-weeknd-hurry-up-tomorrow-3833499">Lana del Rey的帖子是“ The Abyss”的一个隐藏功能，《 The Abyss》</a>是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现的。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亚伯“ the the Weeknd” Tesfaye和Lana del Rey" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/weeknd-del-rey@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana del Rey</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">Weeknd</a>的新专辑“ Purrin Up明天”中作为隐藏功能。在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463"><b>周末 - &#39;Dawn FM&#39;评论：深情的明星与希望和事后见识</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>该记录标志着歌手的“黎明FM”三部曲的第三章也是最后一章，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-delays-new-album-hurry-up-tomorrow-due-to-los-angeles-wildfires-3828567">上周被推迟</a>后通过XO和Republic分享了今天（1月31日）。</p><p>唱片中令人惊讶的一件事是Lana del Rey的意外贡献，他出现在曲目“深渊”上。</p><p>尽管她在这首歌中仍然没有信用，但她的标志性嗓音在脱衣舞，钢琴主导的曲目上听到。</p><p>这不是两人第一次联手。早在2017年，《周末》与德尔·雷伊（Del Rey）合作，从她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lana-del-rey-lust-life-review-2116220">“欲望生活”</a>专辑中的冠军曲目中，两年前她出现在他的2015年曲目“囚犯”上。后者出现在他的大二专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-the-weeknd-16229-311093">《疯狂的美女》中。</a></p><p> “夏季悲伤”的歌手只是专辑中的少数合作之一，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future">Future</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-and-the-machine">Flue + The Machine</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anitta">Anitta</a>的曲目列表中的其他演出。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Weeknd-深渊（音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S3ncfrQPpjs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>正如<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/the-weeknd-lana-del-rey-hurry-up-tomorrow-the-abyss-1235888403/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Billboard</a></em>所强调的那样，另一个惊喜是因为先前发行的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-walks-towards-the-light-in-new-dancing-in-the-flames-video-3793330">“ Dancing In the Flames”</a>明显从最终的跟踪清单中遗漏，这导致猜测是在最后一分钟被废弃还是将其设置为作为一部分一个单独的项目。</p><p>歌手出于对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">洛杉矶野火的</a>受害者的尊重而推迟了这张唱片。上周，他还上了社交媒体宣布取消了他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-announces-hurry-up-tomorrow-and-one-night-only-stadium-show-in-los-angeles-3816568">在加利福尼亚州玫瑰碗的仅一晚音乐会</a>，该音乐会定于1月25日。</p><p> “出于对洛杉矶县人民的尊重和关注，我将取消原定于1月25日举行的玫瑰碗音乐会。这座城市一直是我灵感的深刻来源，在这个困难时期，我的想法与受到影响的每个人都受到影响。”他说。</p><p> “鉴于此，我还决定将专辑的发行推向1月31日。我的重点仍然放在支持这些社区的康复，并在重建时帮助他们令人难以置信的人。” </p><figure id="attachment_3791667" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791667" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791667" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil.jpg" alt="亚伯“ The Weeknd” Tesfaye于2024年9月7日在巴西圣保罗举行的Morumbis的“下班后Til Dawn Tour”期间在舞台上演出。学分：Wagner Meier/Getty Images for Live Nation" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Weeknd-Brazil-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791667" class="wp-caption-text"> “ Weeknd”在2024年在巴西圣保罗演出：Wagner Meier/Getty Images for Live Nation</figcaption></figure><p> 5月，该唱片将伴随着同名长篇电影， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-announces-release-date-for-hurry-up-tomorrow-film-3824134">由Weeknd，Jenna Ortega和Barry Keoghan主演</a>。它被描述为专辑的“扩展”。</p><p>除了确认新项目的细节外，《周刊》还讨论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-on-why-he-wants-to-retire-the-moniker-ive-overcome-every-challenge-as-this-persona-3828072">他计划退休他的著名绰号</a>，并说这并不意味着他正在退休。 “一切都需要感觉像是一个挑战。对我而言，《周末》，无论是什么，它都已经掌握了。”他说。</p><p> “没有人会比我更好，我不会比现在做得更好。我认为我已经克服了这个角色，这就是为什么我对这部电影感到非常兴奋的原因，因为我喜欢这个挑战。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-hidden-feature-on-the-abyss-the-weeknd-hurry-up-tomorrow-3833499">Lana del Rey的帖子是“ The Abyss”的一个隐藏功能，《 The Abyss》</a>是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现的。</p> ;
